response.overview: This collection immediately covers three decades, beginning with a pair of 1940s stripteases, followed by 1950s stars Bobbie Reynolds and Barbara Lyles, and capped by the 1960s’ Tammy Sanders. After that we settle into a 1950s groove of indoor and outdoor modeling, with a family-style American Sunbathing Association promo, Waterfall Fun, thrown into the mix for good measure. After a clip from the naked cowgirl school of cinema, William H. Door sends us a gem. In Party Nudes Real, Joanne Arnold leads a cast of six beauties posing in a temple-like setting at Corriganville movie ranch. Then follows an eclectic mix of 1950s Malibu, a beehive blonde, a “tiki” bedroom, and a quartet of color loops from the swinging ’60s.
response.title: Nudie Cuties: Volume 6
